description.value: The Rainswell is surrounded by a thick foggy mist. Creatures in within a 15 foot aura are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.DmAIPqOBomZ7H95W]{Concealed}. This cloud is suppressed if the Rainswell fails a saving throw against a spell or effect with the Fire or Air keyword. If the aura is dispersed, it returns automatically at the end of the Rainswell's turn.

rules.text: The aura of mist is suppressed if the Rainswell fails a saving throw against a spell or effect with the air or fire trait. It returns automatically at the end of the Rainswell's turn.

description.value: The Rainswells Aura of Mist becomes freezing cold. Enemies in the aura must make a @Check[fortitude|dc:25|basic] save take @Damage[3d8[cold]|options:area-damage].
